Impala Platinum 5.5% Wage Offer Rejected by South Africa’s NUM Labor Union

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-06-21T10:51:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-21/impala-platinum-5-5-wage-offer-rejected-by-south-africa-s-num-labor-union.html
Impala Platinum Holdings Ltd. (IMP) ’s
offer to increase wages by 5.5 percent has been rejected by
 South Africa ’s National Union of Mineworkers.  The labor union wants between 13.5 percent and 14 percent
depending on job category, it said in an e-mailed statement
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  